 - {s}  ADDED   FrameIHack.

 - {s}  ADDED   BorderBlank for Kickstart 2.x.

(21-Nov-95)

 - {s}  FIXED   bug in CycleScreens Back2Front if only one screen was open.

(19-Nov-95)

 - {s}  FIXED   Enforcer-hits and crash on 68000 in PropHack in combination
                with gtlayout.library.

(18-Nov-95)

 - {s}  FIXED   bug in restoresystem-hotkey.

